description: Integrated SqExcelWeb FastAPI proxy to resolve CORS issues with Seeq API calls
changes: Added Vercel proxy domain to manifest.xml AppDomains
Replaced direct Seeq API client with proxy client
All Seeq API calls now route through https://sq-excel-web.vercel.app
Resolved CORS issues by using server-side SPy module
Enhanced authentication flow through proxy server
